    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/7df76f5f00e513bdae640c2191001c68.poster.avif?t=1724002202\" width=610 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/7df76f5f00e513bdae640c2191001c68.webm?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/7df76f5f00e513bdae640c2191001c68.mp4?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/14cf95a9cffec907a0575ffe8d3148f1.avif?t=1724002202\" width=612 height=103 /></span><br>Dive into an <strong>graphic novel inspired ultra-violent escape mission</strong> - to survive the underworld and blast your way through ravaging mutant hordes before they feed their thirst for blood and death. Explore lost ancient ruins and hack your way through the underworld army using the power of awesome long lost weapons and your own grit and will to survive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/1a618323033cd8abaeb217e4d8b1fc91.avif?t=1724002202\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/ff33cd4c816066496fd5379d3a2318b4.poster.avif?t=1724002202\" width=610 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/ff33cd4c816066496fd5379d3a2318b4.webm?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/ff33cd4c816066496fd5379d3a2318b4.mp4?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From <strong>captive to stone-cold-killer</strong> - brave the underworld labyrinth and wipe the mutant scum from the pages of existence. Their evil creator bred an army of cannibals, zombies and half-humans wit the sole aim of the destruction of human civilisation. YOU were caught, experimented on, and injected with mutant blood. It's not good s**t.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/fc8b074e10d8b2cacd2047c61ba5b94f.avif?t=1724002202\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/b434d5ada2ca65cf24607e9f734fc05b.poster.avif?t=1724002202\" width=610 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/b434d5ada2ca65cf24607e9f734fc05b.webm?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/b434d5ada2ca65cf24607e9f734fc05b.mp4?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Wield a variety of weapons</strong>, from classic double-barrel shotguns to experimental plasma rifles, and charge head-first into the fast-paced demon-slaying action. Running out of ammo? Grab the trust fire-axe and aim for the skull. There are plenty of ways to cut your way trhough the demon army and your might even find some hidden (yet lethal) gems.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/27329f6ebeab11dbce7c17ccafc6f35a.avif?t=1724002202\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/fa12256c3c3b7381c77bc82b52acedcc.poster.avif?t=1724002202\" width=610 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/fa12256c3c3b7381c77bc82b52acedcc.webm?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/fa12256c3c3b7381c77bc82b52acedcc.mp4?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in <strong>graphic-novel inspired visuals and ultra-violence</strong>. Watch your enemies explode in bright technicolor in a black and white underworld to the tunes of a bone-shaking soundtrack, highlighted only by the cocking of your trusty Smith 'n' Wesson revolver and the blast of buckshot into a charging demon's gut.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/e2c1c8c0fc1152c9f6289a9854ef4f76.avif?t=1724002202\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/3e2a1d473e7406d9f2765a6f68a46524.poster.avif?t=1724002202\" width=610 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/3e2a1d473e7406d9f2765a6f68a46524.webm?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163650/extras/3e2a1d473e7406d9f2765a6f68a46524.mp4?t=1724002202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Survival and escape</strong> depends on your gun-skills and how you use the tools you find to your advantage. Do you favour a head-on charge or a piercing attack on the flank? Do you want to get up close and personal with a blade or do you like to explode skulls from a distance? The choice is yours!<br><br>If you've read this far and you're interested in playing our demo and game first, <strong>hit the wishlist button now!</strong>",
